Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Listen, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:02.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] You don't have to be the greatest man there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Or the best brother that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother... Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...be the one to make them laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mind if I stay for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER A] See? I thought that'd make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[OLD MAN A] No! Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[THUG B] Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[VILLAGER C] Get back here! --[VILLAGER D] Thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:00.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER B] Somebody please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[THUG A] Hey, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That was too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[THUGS grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[THUG B] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:32.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat! Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[THUG B yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sorry, was I in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] The year is 1879.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:58.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Japan is amidst great transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,An uprise in crime and unrest herald this chaotic time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,With a monster known to emerge every 300 years destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the skies over Shiga have never been more clear or vibrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[wooden sticks clashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The prison's moving to Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:20.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, it has vast, open spaces with a limited population.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:25.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They plan to incarcerate the more dangerous convicts there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Guess that means the end of Gokumonjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Afraid so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It'll be decommissioned before too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I received official notice yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu will disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] The Yamainu mandate was to destroy the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Needless to say, with the serpent gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ministry of the Right, Lord Iwakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,no longer requires our services.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] What happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Many of us have been given the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to join various military ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Inukai and Shi are hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Are you joining the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Eventually, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,For me, protecting and defending our nation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,is the only true contentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Please continue to train me until you've joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Shiga may be losing Gokumonjo and a fierce group
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,of warriors, but not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm almost head of our shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka won't be the strongest brother forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get too cocky. Break's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His physical strength is improving alongside the mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His skills continue to flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Did you prepare something for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's good for the constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I hope he'll enjoy every morsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[BOTAN] I'm certain he will find it memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hi, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You scared me, Hirari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I gave my notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:30.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I won't waste a moment of my life being away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your forethought is lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How will you make a life for yourself now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HIRARI] Don't worry. I have savings, I can feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But that isn't the issue, Hirari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It was nice seeing you both...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go inside and see Soramaru now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of course. Sorry for keeping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Take care, you two. --[HIRARI] Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI, SORAMARU grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think she's uncomfortable here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Must you continue to miss what is so painfully obvious, Hirari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She's a Fuuma. I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One whose base is the Kumou Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we'll sit and chat over tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh... Well, you sure are spending a lot of your time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,with this strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She has no home. No kin or comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nothing of her old life can be returned to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yet here, no longer donned in shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,she smiles easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She's going to face so much doubt and uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She will fumble as she learns to accept our support,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but she is nonetheless endearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want to see her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want to see that smile of hers more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI, SORAMARU grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:59.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell me... How's he been doing lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Pretty much the same, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Tenny! You've got a visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] 'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Hope you're decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How're you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Missing him? It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Look who's back. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm just not used to it, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There is no getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is Nishiki with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:51.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Uh... She's out shopping... for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You promised you would do the cooking tonight, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know, and I tried to talk her out of it, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It'll be another disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] How many times do I have to tell you to leave me alone--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] For once, would you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[SORAMARU] DÃ©jÃ  vu. --[TENKA] I said no, Kiiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Tenka, would you stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenny, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] I'll be out for a bit! Don't wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Stop doing that inside the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Figured you'd be training with Sosei today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] We just finished up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] I see. Sorry for the hysterics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're just grateful that you care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenny's acting strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Something's very wrong. I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Failed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:11.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sadly. I don't know why thought I could do it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] I know all too well that some things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--can't be helped. --[SORAMARU] Kiiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We deserve the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is it that's upsetting him so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] He hasn't said anything about it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible not to notice how livid Tenka gets
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,when the Yamainu come to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] I've noticed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're right. You both deserve to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your brother carries a heavy burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...for those he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] It all began about 11 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:11.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] 89... 90... 91...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:19.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...92... 93... 94... 95...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...96... 97...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't stop, Takamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,98... Faster, Ashiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fight through the aches and pains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If this training is enough stop you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,what chance do you have of destroying the Orochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,99... 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think you're done? 30 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP] Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:51.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] 1... 2... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:59.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...4... 5... 6... 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:04.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...8... 9... 10...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] This hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[SOSEI laughs] --Gah! You're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[TENKA laughs] --[TAIKO] Knock it off, Sosei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] It wasn't me, sir! It was Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Kiiko, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Don't drag me into one of your squabbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[yelps] --[SOSEI] Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:29.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[slapping] --[TENKA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's enough, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI, TENKA] Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Still have some energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How about five laps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Go around the oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka and Sosei, do ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,On your feet, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:53.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is their youth that gives them such promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is. What's your assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI] The progress of strength and body continue to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[INUKAI] They need more experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,About those laps... We don't have to run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You had better catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] A recurrent manifestation of the great
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,snake, Orochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,led to the formation of a secret unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're called the Yamainu squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:30.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Heroes working in obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu will save the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I hate running!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Anyone else starving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So what do you say, old man? Should we feed these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Suppose everybody here's earned grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Dinner at our place tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,First thing's first. I need a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And there he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Always the first one to leave every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're taking it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Each of us has a modus operandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Taiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:17.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There's a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD A] We're not joking here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up or we kill the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD B] You better meet our demands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ONLOOKERS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] A hostage situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:35.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Appears so, sir. Desperate, common criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well. Their demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It involves Gokumonjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TSUCHIYA] They make up the remains of a pretty big
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,gang of thieves and bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If we free the rest of their men,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,they'll release the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KITAMURA] Taiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We don't want these dangerous men
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,back on our streets, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...we don't want the girl harmed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:57.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think you can handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Now's the time to prove yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:08.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saving her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[OFFICER A] Hey! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA grunts] Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:18.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[OFFICER A] It's his little sister that's the hostage, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] If you're not gonna do anything about it, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just give them what they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If he's calling you "sir," that means you're in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:30.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,doesn't it? She has to get out of that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She has to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please do whatever it takes to bring her back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're a good brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You'll see her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What're we dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ashiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:10.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Every one of them has a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Long swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One has a gun on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Firearms complicate things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Harder to plan around with a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where's the girl located?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] They've got her tied up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,right at the back of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Which makes just swooping in to grab her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's quite the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] What're you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please... Don't waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TSUCHIYA] Hey, kid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You can't keep sneaking off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KITAMURA] Everybody get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] As far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the situation goes beyond a simple rescue mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[INUKAI] We're with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TSUCHIYA] Please just trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN B grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN SPY B] Yamainu are on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Everyone inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Get ready for a fight, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want them found this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD A] This is the last thing we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If the Yamainu have found a way to slip inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,we're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C] Calm down. There's only seven of them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,and we've got twice that many guys out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And let's not forget about our little hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN C grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN C yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN G yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN C yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[INUKAI, RONIN D grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN E] Take this--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Hey, there. Ready to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HOSTAGE yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:00.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:09.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Damnit, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:13.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:21.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RONIN HEAD C yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Father! --Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:31.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Kiiko, go see to his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They were expecting the squad and that left
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:42.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,every one of you vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:44.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You opened yourself to an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A bystander in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He was the one that warned their lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:54.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:55.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] We're the Yamainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:08.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yama... inu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:26.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Welp, that's our cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:28.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys! Dinner isn't gonna eat itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:39.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well you haven't been going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Makes wonder where you've been sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:47.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Don't see how that's your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:51.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Watch the attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:53.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm your mentor and guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:55.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your safety is my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:57.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Fine, you wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:00.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I stay with whatever girl I happen to be with that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:03.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ashiya, I'm just trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's what family does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:06.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Don't talk to me about family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:08.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You don't know the first thing about mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:12.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] I'll lend you an ear if you want to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:13.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Yeah, not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:15.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Well that's too bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:16.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:23.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not just you, but all of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:26.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu share laughter, burden, and fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:29.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's foolish to think otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:31.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to tell me all your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:33.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What we need from you is trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.40,0:24:38.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Every single one of you already has mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.85,0:24:44.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:50.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.79,0:24:52.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] You come from a long line of Onmyo mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.72,0:24:54.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.16,0:24:56.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your mystic abilities are unmatched as a scout,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.99,0:24:59.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but what use are those magics in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:03.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think it's about time we found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.87,0:25:09.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] And here I thought training was done for the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.07,0:25:11.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but if seeing an onmyouji fight is what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.43,0:25:32.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...it's what you'll get!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.93,0:25:35.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.47,0:25:42.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You lack focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.94,0:25:44.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA gasps, yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:48.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:50.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] You're too dependent on your Shikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.01,0:25:52.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Save me the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:54.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Get to the point already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:56.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] If you want to destroy the Orochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:57.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you need to be at your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:58.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.82,0:26:02.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] My leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.16,0:26:04.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's a lot stronger than he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.96,0:26:11.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] You have what it takes to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.83,0:26:12.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.00,0:26:15.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] His resilience is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.57,0:26:17.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He could be the one to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.94,0:26:21.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You of course know why I was chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.88,0:26:23.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,for the Yamainu squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.01,0:26:26.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Same as the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:29.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka Kumou, Sosei Abeno, Kiiko Sasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.95,0:26:34.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Zenzo Inukai, Seiichirou Takamine, maybe even Shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.09,0:26:36.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're all potential vessels for the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:40.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How'd you put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.86,0:26:44.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,"The Yamainu share laughter, burden, and fate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.10,0:26:47.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We were brought together because of the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.10,0:26:49.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If it were one of us, it would be easier, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.81,0:26:55.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Apparently, no one told Mother the big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.91,0:26:58.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Imagine her surprise when learning of my father's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.18,0:27:01.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,connection to the Orochi bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.65,0:27:02.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Abomination!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.19,0:27:05.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:11.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] She couldn't see me as anything other than
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.76,0:27:14.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,a monster after learning the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.63,0:27:17.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Blood ties shouldn't sever so cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.00,0:27:20.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But my mother still left Father and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.84,0:27:23.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Be honest with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:25.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you believe the Orochi is going to choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.58,0:27:29.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.78,0:27:32.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm frightened of the serpent itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:34.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I just know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.72,0:27:37.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know that I'd devour everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.08,0:27:39.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Friends, family, home--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:43.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,anything doomed to cross my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.22,0:27:46.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't want to become the monster she thought me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.83,0:27:48.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't want my mother to feel justified
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.86,0:27:50.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,when it finally happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.13,0:27:55.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--If I-- --[TAIKO] I'll make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.94,0:28:02.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I have what it takes after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.18,0:28:03.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.75,0:28:10.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If it comes down to it, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.05,0:28:15.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, Taiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.69,0:28:16.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I trust you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.29,0:28:21.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ever the virtuous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:23.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Amazing, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.23,0:28:26.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Look, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.87,0:28:28.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If the Orochi chooses me to be the vessel--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.84,0:28:29.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.67,0:28:33.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And should I be chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.24,0:28:35.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd expect you to do the same for me, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.71,0:28:39.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.68,0:28:41.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time we caught up with the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.75,0:28:42.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.93,0:28:52.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:28:54.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...what if it were one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.97,0:29:03.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.14,0:29:06.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Been good for your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.34,0:29:07.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.38,0:29:09.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:13.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tenka, you're soaked to the bone, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:15.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let's get you inside and dry off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:19.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Anybody home, Tenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.95,0:29:20.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KOYUKI] Sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:23.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I think somebody missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.69,0:29:28.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your friends are already inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.10,0:29:29.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I hope we're not imposing or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.96,0:29:31.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KOYUKI] Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:34.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see Ashiya finally coming around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.44,0:29:39.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] What if the Orochi chose Soramaru
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.44,0:29:41.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,or Chutaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.84,0:29:44.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do I have what it takes to... kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:47.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:50.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Open up, buddy! Eat your dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.75,0:29:52.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tenka. Don't force him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.02,0:29:54.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All right! You eat it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.16,0:29:59.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] A good dog does as it's told without forethought.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.19,0:30:01.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu squad is meant to protect their country
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.83,0:30:03.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,and defeat the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:04.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.37,0:30:06.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.17,0:30:12.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Death is not permitted to any Yamainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.01,0:30:16.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No Yamainu shall waver until the Orochi is taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.21,0:30:21.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.45,0:30:24.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:45.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.91,0:30:53.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:55.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.38,0:30:56.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Chutaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:58.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[crying continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.46,0:31:05.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[BOTH crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.37,0:31:21.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[strike] --[TENKA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.78,0:31:23.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.04,0:31:24.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.31,0:31:28.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I said I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.28,0:31:30.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're not doing this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.95,0:31:34.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is your sense of duty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:36.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What about everything we were supposed to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.26,0:31:40.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting. That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.56,0:31:45.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.23,0:31:47.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Sosei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:49.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.84,0:31:52.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,After all that crap about becoming heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.31,0:31:53.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You made me believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.91,0:31:55.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You and your father did!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.51,0:31:57.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't let you throw this away!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.81,0:32:00.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't want you to forget us, Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.21,0:32:02.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu need a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.02,0:32:06.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Then it's a good thing they have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.59,0:32:10.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I was never meant to lead the Yamainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.99,0:32:14.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.83,0:32:16.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.90,0:32:19.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.07,0:32:21.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm just not cut out to be a leader like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.31,0:32:28.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As of this moment, we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.14,0:32:30.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I never want to lay eyes on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:34.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Same goes for anyone else thinking of quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.98,0:32:37.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,With or without you, the Yamainu will endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:41.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:44.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As long as there's a squad, you can count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.89,0:32:46.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If you'll shoulder the burden of leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.46,0:32:48.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll follow you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.40,0:32:51.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Trust me and I'll trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.03,0:32:52.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sound logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.58,0:33:06.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Don't stay behind for my benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.95,0:33:11.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep them together no matter what, Kiiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:14.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.47,0:33:26.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.97,0:33:28.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just a damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.98,0:33:41.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So you're back...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The boys tried waiting up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.58,0:33:45.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Thanks for watching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.62,0:33:48.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[OHTA] All that crying really took a lot out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.32,0:33:49.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They've earned a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.39,0:33:55.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And how're you adjusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:56.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Feeling good, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.10,0:33:58.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Those Orochi cells must be adapting to my body
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.67,0:33:59.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:03.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be certain of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.61,0:34:10.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The experiment only ends one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.11,0:34:12.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure I don't have to tell you this, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.05,0:34:15.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.65,0:34:18.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Reuniting with my parents will be a nice comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.72,0:34:20.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why must you sacrifice yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:28.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] The first thing a child learns is that they are loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.53,0:34:31.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Such concentrated emotion is a lesson in and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.00,0:34:36.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be a big brother now, Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.10,0:34:37.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.30,0:34:38.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's so tiny, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:44.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Being the eldest means making sure they know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.45,0:34:46.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,just as much love as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.45,0:34:48.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:50.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I've got plenty of love to give you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.69,0:34:55.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAIKO] Listen, Tenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.76,0:34:58.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be the greatest man there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.66,0:35:01.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Or the best brother that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.50,0:35:05.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Instead, be the one to make them laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.03,0:35:07.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No matter the problem or worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:09.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you can't let your brothers take life too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.37,0:35:14.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Night, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.61,0:35:16.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I love you with all that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.65,0:35:21.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] So what you're saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.62,0:35:24.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,if it weren't for us, Tenka might not have quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.59,0:35:26.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't concern yourselves too much
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:28.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,thinking about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.19,0:35:29.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I'm certain that worrying about you two
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.79,0:35:31.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,wasn't the only factor at play.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.76,0:35:34.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He had a lot to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.13,0:35:37.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let's just say the love your brother has for you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.40,0:35:39.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,made Tenka's decision an easier one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.17,0:35:45.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Leaving the Yamainu squad was beneficial, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.41,0:35:47.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Orochi chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.07,0:35:49.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If Tenka hadn't left when he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.04,0:35:50.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,he would've been bound by his oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.11,0:35:55.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Tenka Kumou is his father's son, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.75,0:35:59.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] We appreciate how much you all care for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.12,0:36:01.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Obviously, some care more than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.62,0:36:03.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If everything you're saying is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.49,0:36:06.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,why is Tenny so mad at the Yamainu?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.83,0:36:07.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.16,0:36:12.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well... at the very least, he isn't mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.47,0:36:14.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.23,0:36:15.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] I don't think you need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.77,0:36:19.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER E] Stop! Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.44,0:36:21.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.61,0:36:27.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Heavens, are you all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.18,0:36:28.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[OFFICER B] Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.42,0:36:33.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CROWD chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.09,0:36:37.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA chuckles] I'm right as rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.46,0:36:39.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER F] Do be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.43,0:36:40.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:55.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Guess who showed up to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.54,0:36:59.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kiiko keeps visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.45,0:37:01.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The guys come by, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.28,0:37:03.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How does any Yamainu have enough free time
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.22,0:37:04.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to bug me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.85,0:37:08.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm taking long walks and picnics with all my free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.76,0:37:12.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Wish they'd take the hint and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:13.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They were done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.76,0:37:15.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Now I can't get rid of anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.33,0:37:21.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.87,0:37:23.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're just coming around because
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.54,0:37:25.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,they're concerned for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:28.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I mean, I understand why and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:30.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They can see what's happening to me and want to pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.64,0:37:32.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,everything's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.31,0:37:34.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But this whole side of my body is paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.82,0:37:36.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Half of my face is totally numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.85,0:37:39.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can barely manage a smile now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.43,0:37:46.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] No more Orochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.30,0:37:49.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No more Gokumonjo...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.40,0:37:56.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's finished... and now I'm useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.95,0:38:09.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] The last thing either of them needs is a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.55,0:38:12.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.79,0:38:15.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...I should've gone when the Orochi did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:21.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] This is why you've been sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.90,0:38:24.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ever the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.27,0:38:28.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sosei.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.74,0:38:32.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey. Been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.24,0:38:34.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you since the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.81,0:38:36.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is what you're saying the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:40.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you think you should've died alongside the Orochi, Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.25,0:38:42.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Show reverence to the hallowed ground laid here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.52,0:38:44.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your parents deserve that kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.59,0:38:46.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Can't a guy catch a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.82,0:38:49.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of all the people that could've overheard, it had to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.76,0:38:56.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Air out grievances here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.23,0:39:01.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.64,0:39:03.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm not the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.64,0:39:06.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I... made a point to not visit until the Orochi
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.01,0:39:08.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,was no longer a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.64,0:39:10.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How honorable of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.78,0:39:13.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] My vow to your family isn't a joke, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.89,0:39:22.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sosei.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.02,0:39:24.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's this apology for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.89,0:39:26.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're sorry for leaving the squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.73,0:39:29.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Being complicit in Orochi experimentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.30,0:39:31.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Saying asinine things to your parents' headstones?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.67,0:39:33.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stealing my daifuku and lying about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.70,0:39:37.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I could continue, so you'll have to be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.40,0:39:39.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,For all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:41.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,From this apology, a person might infer
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.38,0:39:43.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,that you knew what you were doing wasn't above board.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.78,0:39:45.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What else do you need to hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.28,0:39:49.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Given the chance again,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:51.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,would you walk a path different from that which
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:52.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:55.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't regret protecting my brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.86,0:39:58.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.43,0:40:00.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I hate that I wasn't honest with you about what was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.79,0:40:01.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.93,0:40:05.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I do, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.93,0:40:08.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.54,0:40:12.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Orochi is dead and gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.41,0:40:15.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sosei Abeno's mission has been accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.84,0:40:18.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The man I am now has no interest in old scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.61,0:40:23.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I stand before you as someone ready to begin a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.99,0:40:29.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] A fresh start...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.89,0:40:31.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's just what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.93,0:40:34.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] He's not the only one that could use a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.83,0:40:36.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ain't that right, Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.66,0:40:38.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why are all you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.34,0:40:44.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And what's with the uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.44,0:40:45.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You've been disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.87,0:40:47.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is all this, Kiiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.84,0:40:50.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] I'd think it would be fairly obvious by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.64,0:40:54.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Then again, you never did let me explain, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.51,0:40:56.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The squad has one more matter to see to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.52,0:41:03.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All members are now present.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.79,0:41:07.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Commander of the Yamainu, Sosei Abeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.39,0:41:10.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Second-in-command, Seiichirou Takamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.63,0:41:13.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yamainu, Kiiko Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.67,0:41:16.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Yamainu, Mutsuki Ashiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.54,0:41:19.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yamainu, Zenzo Inukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.51,0:41:22.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI] Yamainu, Shi Qian-Lang.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.61,0:41:24.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yamainu, Rakucho Takeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.42,0:41:30.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Yamainu, Tenka Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:34.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.32,0:41:37.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The eight of us are reporting to you for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.62,0:41:40.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,With the Orochi gone, our mission has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.03,0:41:44.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,To all Yamainu: you are now relieved of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:47.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.60,0:41:49.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Though paths may have faltered...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:52.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...your spirit kept us strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.57,0:41:55.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We'll always be grateful to you and your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.91,0:41:59.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu squad strived to maintain the honor
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:01.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you bestowed upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.82,0:42:05.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am pleased to report not a single member has been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.72,0:42:07.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,because of you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.82,0:42:11.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're the reason we're all still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.56,0:42:12.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There's no disputing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.86,0:42:16.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You will not be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.47,0:42:21.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Master Taiko Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.94,0:42:26.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We are forever thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.89,0:42:47.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.93,0:42:49.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.63,0:42:51.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why not do it among friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.01,0:43:04.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.48,0:43:10.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Have I--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:11.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was this my best?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.89,0:43:15.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.02,0:43:17.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] The pain was excruciating.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.59,0:43:21.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:26.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] And it wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.10,0:43:28.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.84,0:43:33.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] But no matter how much I cried or screamed for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.07,0:43:34.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.84,0:43:36.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You weren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.08,0:43:37.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.11,0:43:38.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I tried my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.15,0:43:46.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was it enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.29,0:43:49.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.06,0:43:58.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.70,0:44:00.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Chutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.00,0:44:03.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're more than enough, Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.77,0:44:05.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My brother's the best in the world, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.94,0:44:08.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The absolute best and I don't care who knows it, Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.88,0:44:10.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.71,0:44:12.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey... What're you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.01,0:44:15.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're here, so we're here, sir! Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.78,0:44:17.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.62,0:44:18.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Because you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.72,0:44:19.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.99,0:44:23.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come back! You can't just leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.76,0:44:25.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nobody is leaving you, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.89,0:44:28.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Haven't you realized that yet, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.33,0:44:30.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How much proof do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:33.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.33,0:44:35.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let's get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.74,0:44:38.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're having beef hotpot, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.10,0:44:39.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] But Nishiki's making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.97,0:44:41.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Who let that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.84,0:44:43.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.11,0:44:44.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.11,0:44:46.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We should hurry. It'll be dark before too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.91,0:44:47.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep up, Chutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.98,0:44:48.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.88,0:44:50.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.18,0:44:52.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.22,0:44:53.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.86,0:44:57.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.96,0:45:01.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey... Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.14,0:45:20.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Well damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.05,0:45:22.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,These boys are turning into men.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.68,0:45:24.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,When the hell did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.76,0:45:29.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.92,0:45:32.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We love you! We'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.36,0:45:33.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.39,0:45:35.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.81,0:48:39.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.91,0:48:41.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I thought I told you not to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.82,0:48:43.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.25,0:48:46.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's a celebration, and that means booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.46,0:48:54.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenny, I don't want you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.43,0:48:58.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Still leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.47,0:49:03.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Spent my whole life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.14,0:49:04.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's past time I saw the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.47,0:49:09.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.08,0:49:12.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There's no arguing with him once he's made up his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.11,0:49:14.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] Will you be all right on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.05,0:49:16.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm hurt you even have to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.88,0:49:19.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not like he's traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.29,0:49:20.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP] Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.55,0:49:22.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.39,0:49:24.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a solo trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.26,0:49:25.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.96,0:49:28.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I could use a holiday and you could use the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:30.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.10,0:49:32.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There is no point in arguing with her, Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.43,0:49:34.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Could be a lot worse, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.23,0:49:36.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI] I hear wedding bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.40,0:49:38.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I get to decide all the destinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.01,0:49:40.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.41,0:49:42.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] Where'll your first stop be?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.38,0:49:43.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.98,0:49:45.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Excellent question.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.35,0:49:54.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.02,0:49:56.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.32,0:49:58.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hard not to think about where he is right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.19,0:49:59.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.30,0:50:03.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.95,0:50:25.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA NINJA] Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.12,0:50:27.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're ready to leave when you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.25,0:50:28.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Very good.
